<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[cut chicken in strips and marinade at least 20 m, turning occasionally]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[coat the chicken with first lot of cornstarch]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[make batter with other cornstarch and remaining ingredients (use water if too thick) ]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[coat chicken and deep fry in really hot oil, 5m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[remove oil, wipe wok, pour back 2 tbsp oil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[put sauce ingredients minus cornstarch into wok, bring to boil, then reduce, 30s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[add cornstarch, 30 s]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[pour over chicken and serve]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
